             was indicted for <rs id="t18050220-37-off221" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18050220-37-off221" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050220-37-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050220-37-cd222" type="crimeDate">12th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050220-37-off221 t18050220-37-cd222"></join>, four pounds weight of soap, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050220-37-victim397" type="victimName">
                     John-Floyd 
                     Hopkins
                  <interp inst="t18050220-37-victim397" type="surname" value="Hopkins"></interp>
